genresAdvancedInfo.name: musica etnica
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Musica etnica - This genre consists of traditional music from various ethnic groups around the world. The music often uses traditional instruments and is rooted in cultural practices and beliefs. Musica etnica celebrates diversity and the richness of different cultures, bringing people together through the universal language of music.
